{"tid":1517594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 唔 好 再 廣 傳 檢 舉 藍 絲 TG channel","createTime":"2019-08-30T03:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:08:14.000Z","uid":38737,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"287e3f7dd4b1091bed7cd81a57021463e2604b87","tid":1517594,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"自從71衝入立法會<br />\n藍絲開好多Tg channel玩起底<br />\n父母搵仔女<br />\n防治蟲鼠<br />\netc<br />\n<br />\n成日見到有人廣傳叫人幫手檢舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGCh4xZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGCh4xZ.png&h=9515d14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n唔好咁天真<br />\nTg唔同fb ig<br />\n唔係多人report就收皮<br />\n就算200萬人report都係冇用<br />\n基本上只有色情內容先會令一個channel收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以你班友叫人report係冇撚用<br />\n仲會做埋豬隊友</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\n你地咁做只會幫人地宣傳<br />\n有啲人又會手多撳埋個join button<br />\n變相幫人地谷subscriber<br />\n本來呢啲channel冇人知冇人睇<br />\n本來得幾十subscribers<br />\n就係你地幫人宣傳<br />\n變到幾百幾千subscribers<br />\n對家見到自己搞個channel越嚟越多人睇<br />\n咁咪越有心機繼續做繼續出post繼續管理囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n你地咁做係散播緊白色恐佈<br />\n本來只有藍絲先會subscribe本來只有佢地先會睇<br />\n就算真係有手足唔小心俾佢地起底<br />\n最多咪就係得佢地知 得佢地睇到<br />\n你咁樣貼link幫人宣傳<br />\n咪搞到自己人睇到 甚至被起底者本人都睇到<br />\n俾著你俾人起底 梗係希望越少人知 最好連自己都唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應付呢啲channel只有一種方法<br />\n就係冷處理</span></span><br />\n點解林鄭都識冷處理<br />\n大家唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCZoZKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCZoZKu.png&h=f27328ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再俾我見到你地做豬隊友</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922d32f10391a0cf4585b8f2d54ffb63990a4f31","tid":1517594,"uid":78651,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:21:03.000Z","msg":"俾啲色情資訊佢有無得諗"},{"pid":"cb678190b7b0b9e7b540238b9694d62d705288d7","tid":1517594,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立即普選 否則攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1f986d19c7c8c40763cf15010f0a66022bb56f4b","tid":1517594,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:22:58.000Z","msg":"推到全世界都學識冷處理"},{"pid":"b2e84202f5ffa9b3cd1733c399ee97f8c97e685e","tid":1517594,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立即普選 否則攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"89f4aca743deb1e29b480fdf6d3681bfae34912d","tid":1517594,"uid":178078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"咁不如入去瘋狂PO J圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9992b0d82729d0cbc7b304c32a56df3a82505e15","tid":1517594,"uid":258159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"阻你一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Tb3eS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Tb3eS